### Builder Pattern

Builder separates object construction from its representation, enabling step-by-step creation of complex objects. Use it when objects have many optional parameters or complex initialization logic.

```typescript
class UserBuilder {
  private user: any = {};
  setName(name: string) { this.user.name = name; return this; }
  setEmail(email: string) { this.user.email = email; return this; }
  setRole(role: string) { this.user.role = role; return this; }
